    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个从代码提交到服务上线的完整流程图。核心是让开发团队看清楚他们的提交是怎么变成线上服务的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DEV",
        "CI",
        "ENV"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那我把流程分成三大块：开发者侧、CI/CD流水线、还有最终部署环境。开发者那边具体包含哪些动作？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DEV"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "开发者这边其实就是一个起点——提交代码或者提PR。用一个节点概括就行，叫\"Commit / PR\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "DEV"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把开发者子图画出来，DEV框里放Commit/PR节点。接下来CI/CD部分你打算拆几步？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DEV",
        "A"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "CI/CD要三步：Build、Test、Deploy。测试环节经常出问题，得单独标出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CI",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D"
